quran[8]{c,v,t,f}:
  10,26,"Rere àti àlékún (oore) wà fún àwọn tó ṣe rere. Eruku tàbí ìyẹpẹrẹ kan kò níí bò wọ́n lójú mọ́lẹ̀. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni èrò inú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra. Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀.",""
  10,27,"Àwọn tó sì ṣ’iṣẹ́ aburú, ẹ̀san aburú bí irú rẹ̀ (ni ẹ̀san wọn). Ìyẹpẹrẹ sì máa bò wọ́n mọ́lẹ̀. Kò sí aláàbò kan fún wọn lọ́dọ̀ Allāhu. (Wọ́n máa dà bí) ẹni pé wọ́n fi apá kan òru tó ṣókùnkùn bò wọ́n lójú pa. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni èrò inú Iná. Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀.",""
  10,28,"Àti pé (rántí) Ọjọ́ tí A óò kó gbogbo wọn jọ, lẹ́yìn náà A óò sọ fún àwọn tó bá Allāhu wá akẹgbẹ́ pé: “Ẹ dúró pa sí àyè yín, ẹ̀yin àti àwọn òrìṣà yín.” Nítorí náà, A yà wọ́n sí ọ̀tọ̀ọ̀tọ̀. Àwọn òrìṣà wọn sì wí pé: “Àwa kọ́ ni ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún.”",""
  10,29,"Nítorí náà, Allāhu tó ní Ẹlẹ́rìí láààrin àwa àti ẹ̀yin pé àwa jẹ́ aláìmọ̀ nípa ìjọ́sìn yín (tí ẹ̀ ṣe fún wa).”",""
  10,30,"Níbẹ̀ yẹn, ẹ̀mí kọ̀ọ̀kan máa dá ohun tó ṣe síwájú mọ̀. Wọn yó sì da wọ́n padà sọ́dọ̀ Allāhu Olúwa wọn Òdodo. Ohun tí wọ́n ń dá ní àdápa irọ́ sì di òfo mọ́ wọn lọ́wọ́.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-’Ani‘ām; 6:24."
  10,31,"Sọ pé: “Ta ni Ó ń pèsè fún yín láti inú sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀? Ta ni Ó ní ìkápá lórí ìgbọ́rọ̀ àti ìríran? Ta ni Ó ń mú alààyè jáde láti ara òkú, tí Ó tún ń mú òkú jáde láti ara alààyè? Ta sì ni Ó ń ṣe ètò ọ̀rọ̀ (ẹ̀dá)?” Wọn yóò wí pé: “Allāhu” Nígbà náà, sọ pé: “Ṣé ẹ ò níí bẹ̀rù (Rẹ̀) ni?”",""
  10,32,"Ìyẹn ni Allāhu Olúwa yín Òdodo. Kí sì ni ó ń bẹ lẹ́yìn Òdodo bí kò ṣe ìṣìnà? Nítorí náà, báwo ni wọ́n ṣe ń ṣẹ́rí yín kúrò níbi òdodo?",""
  10,33,"Báyẹn ni ọ̀rọ̀ Olúwa rẹ ṣe wá sí ìmúṣẹ lórí àwọn tó ṣèbàjẹ́ pé dájúdájú wọn kò níí gbàgbọ́.",""
